Talking To People - messengers
Encrypting Email - email is insecure, gnugpg better than nothing
Sending Files - Magic Wormhole
Encrypting Backups - tarsnap or full disk encryption
Signing Packages - minisign
Encrypting Application Data - libsodium
Encrypting Files - age like https://github.com/str4d/rage

